high_descs: Move to the toilet.
Pick up the soap on the toilet.
Head to the right and face the sink on the left.
Wet the soap in the left sink with water.
Bring the wet soap back to the toilet on the left.
Put the wet soap back on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put wet soap on the toilet.

high_descs: Walk forward to the toilet.
Pick up the soap from the toilet tank.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Get the soap wet.
Turn right and go back to the toilet.
Put the soap on the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Put wet soap on the toilet tank.

high_descs: Go to the toilet.
Take the pink soap off of the toilet.
Turn and go to the sink on the left.
Put the soap in the sink on the left, turn on the water and pick up the soap.
Turn and go to the toilet.
Put the soap on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed soap on the toilet.

high_descs: Move a bit to the left to face the toilet.
Pick the soap up from the toilet.
Move to the left to face the sink on the left.
Put the soap in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the soap back up.
Move to the left and face the toilet.
Put the soap on the back of the toilet.
Walk forward to the toilet
Pick up the soap bar from the top of the toilet
Move a few feet right and turn to face the left most sink
Rinse the soap under water in the sink and remove it
Move slightly left and face toward the toilet
Put the soap bar on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: Put the rinsed soap bar on the toilet

high_descs: Move closer to the toilet.
Pick up the bar of soap that is on the back of the toilet.
Move to the sink that is to the right of the toilet.
Rinse off the bar of soap in the sink before pulling it back out.
Move back over to the toilet.
Place the bar of soap to the right of the lotion dispenser on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move a wet bar of soap to the back of the toilet.
